      "message": "Only argument count is checked, not types.\nSuggest adding:\n```\n  static_assert((std::is_convertible_v\u003cArgs\u0026\u0026, ReturnTypes\u003e \u0026\u0026 ...),\n                \"deferred_reply::send argument types must be \"\n                \"convertible to ReturnTypes\");\n```",
